{"tid":51090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"持槍劫性用品店 憨匪被女店員掟假JJ擊退","createTime":"2016-12-23T02:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T03:21:16.000Z","uid":15209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6adcfeca8647a796ea06f092129714ac864c8e","tid":51090,"uid":15209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:40:52.000Z","msg":"近日美國加利福尼亞州有一家情趣用品店突然闖進一名持槍的劫匪，作勢威逼女店員交錢，點知兩名金髮索女「唔惹少」，對匪徒的叫囂也毫不屈服，仲勇猛掟出2條假陽具，成功嚇退匪徒。事後女店員受訪稱早知道匪徒拿的是假槍，一點都不驚。<br />\n <br />\n案件發生在15日，從閉路電視可見，一名男子持槍進入情趣用品店後，脅迫店員交出財物，沒想到櫃檯的金髮店員仲惡過他，呵斥匪徒。<br />\n<br />\n匪徒見威逼不成，行埋櫃檯動手想搶錢。此時另一名女店員出手相助，掟出一條假陽具正中匪徒的頭部，其後又掟多條，居然成功嚇退匪徒。<br />\n<br />\n其中位店員艾美事後表示，她早發現匪徒拿的是假槍，「那個男子拿著一把槍走進商店時，我以為他在開玩笑，我想說他應該是想嚇嚇我們而已，但我後來發現，他應該是來真的！」艾美更表示當時一點都不害怕，「只是覺得很生氣而已！他竟然敢進到我管的商店裡搶劫！」另一名店員則表示：「我覺得他根本就是膽小鬼。」目前警方還在根據閉路電視提供的線索追捕匪徒。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-plastic-post/1661890-%E6%8C%81%E3%80%8C%E6%A7%8D%E3%80%8D%E6%89%93%E5%8A%AB%E6%80%A7%E7%94%A8%E5%85%B7%E5%BA%97-%E6%86%A8%E5%8C%AA%E8%A2%AB%E5%A5%B3%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%E6%8E%9F%E5%81%87jj%E6%93%8A%E9%80%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F9-plastic-post%2F1661890-%25E6%258C%2581%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25A7%258D%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%258A%25AB%25E6%2580%25A7%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2585%25B7%25E5%25BA%2597-%25E6%2586%25A8%25E5%258C%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258E%259F%25E5%2581%2587jj%25E6%2593%258A%25E9%2580%2580&d=9XDN3Mps%2F8vLzcjwtXctS0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=a366c1fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-plastic-post/1661890-%E6%8C%81%E3%80%8C%E6%A7%8D%E3%80%8D%E6%89%93%E5%8A%AB%E6%80%A7%E7%94%A8%E5%85%B7%E5%BA%97-%E6%86%A8%E5%8C%AA%E8%A2%AB%E5%A5%B3%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%E6%8E%9F%E5%81%87jj%E6%93%8A%E9%80%80</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OS3dRL2g71g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOS3dRL2g71g&d=9XDN3Mps%2F8vLzcjwtXctS0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=a67b789e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OS3dRL2g71g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">掟假JJ</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3140c9020718f5346510aaeae7b90269f085021a","tid":51090,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:42:54.000Z","msg":"索女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fda9c7b4562aed6e960efe56c4645b36bb38c6","tid":51090,"uid":24063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:49:10.000Z","msg":"可以拎黎做av劇情<br />\n憨匪遇痴女<br />\n打劫唔成 比痴女女店員迫做愛 仲要玩哂所有性用品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d0c1c23f2380d3c40c00e636865e72c21ecaff","tid":51090,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:55:40.000Z","msg":"Dum 碌鳩掟賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003715e47a27c1de539de927ece8f6ee3086291f","tid":51090,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:58:14.000Z","msg":"比比比 比條撚你呀 英文點講"},{"pid":"7499b65ca50e92e56fa3f41105c66473a0b39af6","tid":51090,"uid":24010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:04:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b1a39efbe69de4a2ab6ab87f6f2ca465bccee99","tid":51090,"uid":24063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Dum 碌鳩掟賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkg